Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.80,0:00:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}小狗汪汪地說道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.16,0:00:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我去烤餅乾了喲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.19,0:00:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}小鴨呱呱地說道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.84,0:00:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}那我就去泡紅茶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.49,0:00:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}小羊咩咩地說道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.37,0:00:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我去做蛋糕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.41,0:00:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}這時狐狸先生來了 Kon Kon地問道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.79,0:00:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}這裡錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.87,0:00:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}真正的狐狸叫起來是「汪」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.12,0:00:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}是嗎 不是「Kon Kon」嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.53,0:00:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}真的真的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.83,0:00:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}前陣子在咖啡店碰上有聽到過
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.47,0:00:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}哎 在咖啡店嗎 怎麼會呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.54,0:00:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}不過大家都覺得是「Kon Kon」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.35,0:00:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}所以這樣也行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.07,0:00:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.60,0:00:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}於是大家和和睦睦地舉辦了茶會
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.05,0:00:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}完
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.33,0:00:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}嗯 好有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.50,0:00:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.64,0:01:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我們回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.84,0:01:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.52,0:01:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}你們在做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.88,0:01:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}這是什麼 好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.81,0:01:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}全都是媽媽畫的喲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.10,0:01:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}好厲害 伯母畫得真好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.35,0:01:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}謝謝誇獎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.07,0:01:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}跟專業的一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.76,0:01:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}咦 原來真琴你不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.16,0:01:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}媽媽是繪本畫家
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.57,0:01:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}是這樣的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.44,0:01:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}還真的是專業的？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.64,0:01:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.47,0:01:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}剛剛是請千夏幫忙確認一下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.29,0:01:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}小孩子看了會不會覺得有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.90,0:01:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}媽媽寫的故事真的很有品味呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.77,0:01:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}很有才華呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.17,0:01:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}承蒙誇獎
