Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.35,0:06:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}可以嗎 好高興
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.59,0:06:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}真好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.10,0:06:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}當然也會幫兩位占卜的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.57,0:06:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}真的嗎 免費嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.36,0:06:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}免費免費
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.46,0:06:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我的占卜基本上是自創的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.08,0:06:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}當成建議來聽就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.70,0:06:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}女孩子真的很喜歡占卜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.92,0:06:22.12,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}怎麼占卜 怎麼占卜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.69,0:06:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}是啊 我的客人也幾乎都是女的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.15,0:06:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}以前不是流行過動物占卜嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.09,0:06:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}確實有呢 我挺喜歡那個的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.39,0:06:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我算出來是獅子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.92,0:06:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我的是狸貓
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.45,0:06:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}挺像的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.80,0:06:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}你們在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.21,0:06:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}千夏當時還太小 所以不知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.94,0:06:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我記得你算出來是天馬
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.16,0:06:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}天馬？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.62,0:06:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}命相天馬的人非常自由
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.03,0:06:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}犬養小姐算出來是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.47,0:06:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}猿猴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.60,0:06:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}跟你完全相反呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.60,0:06:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.24,0:07:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}「犬猿之交」嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.04,0:07:01.89,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}※犬猿之交（犬猿の仲）\N\h{\fscx80\fscy80}日本俗語，指水火不容
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.56,0:07:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}那我們開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.29,0:07:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}有什麼煩惱與迷茫 就大方說出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.82,0:07:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.69,0:07:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我想想…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.70,0:07:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}好像沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.77,0:07:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}哎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.77,0:07:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}請等一下 我再想想
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.38,0:07:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}煩惱 煩惱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.40,0:07:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}請治好我路痴的毛病
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.15,0:07:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}不 占卜是不能治病的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.36,0:07:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.53,0:07:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.08,0:07:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}千夏請說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.67,0:07:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}請問今天晚餐吃什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.74,0:07:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}去問你媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.14,0:07:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}下週就要考試了 該怎麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.26,0:07:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}認真讀書
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.77,0:07:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}果然是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.56,0:07:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}你們還真幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.02,0:07:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}不過這是好事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.62,0:07:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}不然就占卜一下明天的運勢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.30,0:08:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}也好呢 那就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.89,0:08:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我來說明一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.63,0:08:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}首先用雙手把這些小石頭捧起來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.28,0:08:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.19,0:08:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}然後在心裡想著「請告訴我明天的運勢」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.03,0:08:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}同時將石頭丟在這個圓內
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.13,0:08:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我會根據哪種石頭掉在哪來占卜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.07,0:08:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}這叫什麼占卜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.57,0:08:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}投石占卜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.88,0:08:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}真直接
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.95,0:08:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}那麼就…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.01,0:08:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}單數雙數？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.40,0:08:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}你懂的還真多
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.96,0:08:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}電視上有看過
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.34,0:08:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}「出老千出老千 老子要幹掉你」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.15,0:08:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}結果如何 犬養小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.02,0:08:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}石頭顯示出來的有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.01,0:08:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}旅行 意外性 不需要 獨創性
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.77,0:09:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}問題 再會 還有禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.28,0:09:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}大概是你明天出門的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.47,0:09:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}會遇到意想不到的考驗的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.69,0:09:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}但只要通過考驗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.92,0:09:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}就能獲得不小的成果和成長
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.64,0:09:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}大概是這個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.04,0:09:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}明天在學校會碰上不尋常的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.64,0:09:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}說不定呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.09,0:09:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}那下一個換千夏了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.18,0:09:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.26,0:09:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.86,0:09:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}兩面性 傳統 旅行 未知的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.82,0:09:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}愚行 沒意義 寶物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.99,0:09:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}原來如此 原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.39,0:09:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}你明天會碰上一件讓你露出嶄新一面的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.00,0:09:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}而這件事最終將成為千夏的寶物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.23,0:10:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}太好了呢 千夏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.30,0:10:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}嗯 雖然不是很懂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.37,0:10:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}那麼接下來是圭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.39,0:10:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}不過努力還是可以拿高分喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.74,0:10:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}變成漂亮的犬養姐姐了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.94,0:10:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}確實是漂亮的犬養小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.70,0:10:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}真的是漂亮的犬養小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.81,0:10:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}你們說什麼啦 別這樣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.60,0:10:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}時間不早了 我也該告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.59,0:10:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}下次再來玩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.37,0:10:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}謝謝 替我向茜問好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.15,0:10:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我們出門啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.14,0:10:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}占卜會不會中呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.23,0:10:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}好期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.24,0:10:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我嶄新的一面是什麼樣的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.24,0:10:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我應該換個新髮型吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.03,0:11:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}意想不到的考驗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.95,0:11:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}無論如何我都要克服它
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.99,0:11:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}不覺得有點小嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.12,0:11:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}不是不是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.87,0:11:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我只是覺得那央你今天的便當有點小
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.04,0:11:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}你是說這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.33,0:11:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}嗯 畢竟最近變胖了一點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.26,0:11:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}哎 外表完全看不出來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.18,0:11:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}是不是正常發育呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.57,0:11:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}是嗎 但我也想變得更苗條點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.23,0:11:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}現在也在節食
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.38,0:11:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}不好好吃飯對身體不好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.91,0:11:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我奶奶說過 健康的身體會幫女性的魅力加分
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.48,0:11:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}你奶奶還教你這些啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.69,0:11:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}她還說女孩子稍微肉一點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.55,0:11:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}會更受男孩子歡迎呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.29,0:11:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.90,0:11:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}那我還是好好吃飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.92,0:11:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}要吃個煎蛋嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.65,0:11:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}好 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.97,0:12:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我吃飽啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.64,0:12:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}那央 今天有空嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.91,0:12:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}要來我家玩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.72,0:12:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.45,0:12:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我現在在家裡種菜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.70,0:12:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}那還真厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.89,0:12:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}然後我種的毛豆開花了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.96,0:12:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}你見過毛豆的花嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.80,0:12:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}沒看過
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.27,0:12:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}超可愛的 我也想讓那央看一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.00,0:12:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我有時候會懷疑 你真的是女高中生嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.44,0:12:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}哎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.18,0:12:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}有時就像跟老婆婆說話一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.47,0:12:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}哎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.52,0:12:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}姐姐回來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.62,0:12:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}姐姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.17,0:13:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}原來你有姐姐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.87,0:13:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}你姐姐也是魔女嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.49,0:13:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.99,0:13:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}這就是我的菜園
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.68,0:13:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}好厲害 種得有模有樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.61,0:13:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}伯父教了我不少經驗和技巧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.94,0:13:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}那央你看 這就是毛豆開的花
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.20,0:13:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}真的耶 比想像中可愛多了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.07,0:13:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}就說吧 結豆後我分你一些吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.07,0:13:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}真的嗎 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.48,0:13:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}你還種了些什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.39,0:13:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我看看…番茄青椒和玉米吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.24,0:13:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}這些好像是推薦給初學者種的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.30,0:13:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我超喜歡吃番茄
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.51,0:13:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}還有那裡面的是上次拔的曼陀羅草
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.34,0:13:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}那個…很吵的傢伙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.18,0:13:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}就是它
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.70,0:14:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}有書上說把它的葉子栽進土裡 就會長一株新的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.94,0:14:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}所以我正在做實驗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.95,0:14:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}你還想種幾株出來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.72,0:14:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}沒錯 因為它很珍貴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.97,0:14:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}味道都跑出來了 看來長得很大了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.45,0:14:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}對了 那央要不要帶回去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.20,0:14:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}就說我不要了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.48,0:14:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}前陣子才有人教我怎麼用它泡出不苦的茶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.70,0:14:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}並不是味道的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.03,0:14:26.43,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}來看看它長得如何吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.33,0:14:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}真的不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.28,0:14:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我去拿點喝的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.97,0:14:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.91,0:15:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}你來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.47,0:15:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.84,0:15:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我剛剛去看菜園了 好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.96,0:15:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}確實是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.52,0:15:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}什麼時候收成啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.87,0:15:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}七月左右吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.28,0:15:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}真期待
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.87,0:15:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}是時候把茄子種下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.45,0:15:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}以後會越來越忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.60,0:15:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}你還真喜歡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.14,0:15:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}你回來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.31,0:15:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}她怎麼了 好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.98,0:15:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}早安 還有歡迎回家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.84,0:15:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}真琴 你聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.52,0:16:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}姐姐以為阿圭帶女朋友回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.10,0:16:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}以為我是他女朋友嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.75,0:16:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.64,0:16:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}別這樣 那種傢伙根本不是我的菜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.15,0:16:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}別叫我「那種傢伙」呀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.66,0:16:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}看吧 都跟你說不是了 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.49,0:16:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}是位很有趣的姐姐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.28,0:16:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}嗯 姐妹倆都好有個性
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.01,0:16:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}你好 奇多小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.60,0:16:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}這孩子叫什麼名字
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.14,0:16:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}她叫肯尼小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.78,0:16:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}幸會 肯尼小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.12,0:16:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.83,0:16:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}歡迎回家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.08,0:16:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}那央姐今天來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.29,0:16:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}歡迎回家 千夏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.03,0:16:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}真琴姐 看過櫻桃蘿蔔了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.59,0:16:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}差點忘了 長得如何啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.64,0:16:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}應該快成熟了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.41,0:17:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}嗯 看起來已經能吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.38,0:17:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}那就去摘起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.20,0:17:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}你還種櫻桃蘿蔔了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.60,0:17:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}是啊 那央也來幫忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.16,0:17:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.01,0:17:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}阿圭要一起來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.68,0:17:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}不了 現在正到精彩的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.91,0:17:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}那我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.30,0:17:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我小學時也種過櫻桃蘿蔔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.16,0:17:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}有用花盆種嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.58,0:17:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}是啊 種了很多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.90,0:17:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}那央也帶點回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.40,0:17:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}不會種太多了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.90,0:17:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}播種的時候太興奮不禁就…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.46,0:17:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}暫時不用愁沒得吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.07,0:17:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}你們這陣子光吃櫻桃蘿蔔嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.40,0:17:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}能吃完嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.48,0:17:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}本來就計劃送人 或者醃漬保存的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.12,0:17:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}你就放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.16,0:17:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}長得真好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.68,0:17:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}塊頭真大
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.30,0:17:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}好大
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.56,0:17:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}等等洗乾淨就來吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.66,0:18:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}能生吃的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.96,0:18:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.15,0:18:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}對了 那央
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.57,0:18:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我在書上看過 吃櫻桃蘿蔔能消浮腫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.37,0:18:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.74,0:18:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}多吃就能變苗條
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.62,0:18:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}天啊 那也太棒了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.08,0:18:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}而且肌膚也能有光澤
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.28,0:18:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}簡直無敵了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.97,0:18:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}櫻桃蘿蔔可真厲害 我能多拿點嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.12,0:18:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}想拿就拿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.90,0:18:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}咦 白色的？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.13,0:18:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}那是不同種的櫻桃蘿蔔了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.93,0:19:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}還真是大豐收啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.06,0:19:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}還只是一小部分而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.30,0:19:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}要一口氣全採下來也太難了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.11,0:19:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我能嚐一個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.24,0:19:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}請用 大家一起吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.02,0:19:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}為了美麗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.70,0:19:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}為了美麗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.90,0:19:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}你們這是做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.91,0:19:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.91,0:19:32.56,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}好辣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.12,0:19:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}吃這個還要看運氣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.92,0:19:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.95,0:19:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}對了 完全把犬養小姐的占卜給忘記了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.44,0:19:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}意想不到的考驗是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.65,0:19:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}發生什麼考驗了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.75,0:20:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}叮咚噹咚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.64,0:20:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}木幡茜姐姐在等你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.93,0:20:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}請立刻來客廳一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.43,0:20:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}請立刻來客廳一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.17,0:20:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}喲 謝啦謝啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.88,0:20:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}怎麼了呀 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.24,0:20:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}時差沒調整過來 白天一直在睡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.62,0:20:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}現在很清醒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.08,0:20:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}因此…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.69,0:20:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}發禮物時間到啦
