Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.56,0:21:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}很有趣吧 居然還寫著日文
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.99,0:21:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}謝謝…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.44,0:21:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}千夏的禮物也很帥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.88,0:21:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}意想不到的考驗
